07:42.079 --> 07:43.462
Okay.
I'll find 'em.

07:43.547 --> 07:44.663
It'll be fun,
like a game or something.

07:44.798 --> 07:46.665
-Yeah.
-See ya.

07:46.800 --> 07:48.834
So, it's really lucky
that I ran into you,

07:48.969 --> 07:51.303
'cause the insurance
didn't totally cover the damage

07:51.371 --> 07:53.972
to the party bus
and your part's $5,000.

07:55.142 --> 07:57.342
