08:06.403 --> 08:08.103
Look, I'm sorry,
but you did the damage,

08:08.188 --> 08:10.906
so you're gonna have
to figure it out.

08:11.024 --> 08:13.057
Look, this isn't my dream
to have to ask you.

08:13.160 --> 08:14.826
This is really hard.

08:16.997 --> 08:18.396
It doesn't have
to all be at once.

08:18.532 --> 08:20.031
Thank you.

08:20.117 --> 08:22.534
You're welcome.

08:26.006 --> 08:27.756
Ooh, that was rough.

08:28.709 --> 08:30.175
You ready to do the discount?

08:33.764 --> 08:36.398
Hey, mindy, um, I've recently

08:36.466 --> 08:38.233
