the city-- well, it's a lot.

08:41.271 --> 08:43.572
-Uh-huh.
-You know, I'm not sure
if you kept my résumé,

08:43.640 --> 08:44.773
but if you did, you'd know
that I graduated

08:44.858 --> 08:47.409
magna cum laude from nyu and

08:47.477 --> 08:50.161
I've managed
teams of people, so yeah--

08:50.280 --> 08:51.530
I'd love to throw
my hat in the ring for that

08:51.615 --> 08:53.782
-assistant management position.
-(chuckles)

08:53.917 --> 08:56.150
despite what you may have
heard or witnessed,

08:56.253 --> 08:58.753
uh, I think I could
hit this out of the park,

08:58.822 --> 09:01.256
in exchange for just
a small salary bump.

09:01.324 --> 09:02.641
