09:03.710 --> 09:04.793
-What?
-Samantha,

09:04.928 --> 09:06.962
you can't even slice meat.

09:07.047 --> 09:10.098
Okay, it's actually a lot more
difficult than it looks,

09:10.166 --> 09:11.349
and I'm learning
how to slice meat

09:11.468 --> 09:12.667
'cause doris
is a wonderful mentor.

09:12.769 --> 09:13.768
I-I just...

09:13.837 --> 09:16.170
Look, I am in a little bit
of trouble here.

09:16.306 --> 09:19.107
So if there is anything--
like, really anything--

09:19.175 --> 09:21.276
I would just love
the chance to show you

09:21.361 --> 09:23.228
that I can excel here.

09:23.313 --> 09:27.115
