09:41.999 --> 09:43.248
Oh, I thought
you were my burrito.

09:43.366 --> 09:45.500
-Oh.
-Oh, hey.

09:45.636 --> 09:47.335
Hey, sorry, I tried calling.

09:47.421 --> 09:49.804
Oh. Yeah.
We're about to go jogging.

09:49.873 --> 09:51.840
This is samantha.
