10:09.660 --> 10:11.693
-being married
to that character.
-I know,

10:11.828 --> 10:13.862
but be my connie britton
and just give me this five...

10:13.997 --> 10:15.530
Okay, kyle chandler, I love you.
Five minutes.

10:15.666 --> 10:17.165
-Okay, I love you so much.
-Love you back.

10:17.250 --> 10:19.400
-You're my world. I love you.
-I love you. Beyond, beyond.

10:19.536 --> 10:21.536
-Yes.
