10:30.097 --> 10:32.213
She's launching a girl-power
athleisure company.

10:32.299 --> 10:34.549
Girl boss-ton.

10:34.635 --> 10:37.052
Anyway, it's very funny,
it's extremely cute.

10:37.187 --> 10:40.088
-And I think
it's got a great message.
-Plus she's super hot.

10:40.223 --> 10:42.924
