10:59.826 --> 11:01.543
for money again,
'cause she'll own me, so...

11:01.628 --> 11:03.411
Well, the good news
is you don't have to do that.

11:03.497 --> 11:05.714
Oh, okay, good.
What do I do?

11:05.782 --> 11:08.216
Oh, um, I don't know.
(short chuckle)

11:08.301 --> 11:10.218
(short laugh)
what do you mean?

11:10.286 --> 11:11.670
Well, I'm not
your financial advisor.

11:11.755 --> 11:13.555
