11:42.386 --> 11:44.436
All of those problems--
your mom, the money,

11:44.504 --> 11:45.970
your friends, your ex--

11:46.056 --> 11:47.505
those all stem
from your drinking.

11:47.641 --> 11:50.275
So... So what do I do?

11:50.360 --> 11:51.443
Don't drink.

11:51.511 --> 11:53.278
Right.

11:53.346 --> 11:55.230
Okay, so I have
to ask my mom for money.

11:55.315 --> 11:56.681
Ooh, who said that?

11:56.783 --> 11:58.450
Sorry to interrupt.

11:58.518 --> 12:00.652
I'm just grabbing josh.

12:00.737 --> 12:02.487
Thought you guys
would be done now.

12:02.572 --> 12:04.689
So... Hi, baby,

12:04.825 --> 12:06.624
-hi.
-(josh yowls)

12:06.693 --> 12:08.493
hi, joshy boy.

12:10.330 --> 12:12.464
