two more minutes.

12:12.532 --> 12:14.499
Okay.

12:15.635 --> 12:17.802
Okay, you are smart

12:17.871 --> 12:19.387
and you don't need to solve
this problem right now.

12:19.506 --> 12:22.173
The only thing you need
to do is to stay sober today.

12:22.309 --> 12:23.842
One day at a time.

12:23.927 --> 12:25.844
Oh, boy, okay.

12:25.979 --> 12:29.013
Thank you.
Really nice to meet you.

12:29.149 --> 12:30.315
Love the leggings.

12:30.400 --> 12:31.683
Oh my god, thank you.
Wait, don't leave,

12:31.818 --> 12:32.717
don't leave.
I'll get you a pair.

12:32.853 --> 12:33.718
No, honestly, it's fine.

12:33.854 --> 12:34.853
-Take josh.
-Yep.

